e=\"mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-bidi-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><span>1、<spantimes new=\"\" roman\"\'=\"\"> </spantimes></span></span><!--[endif]-->在<span lang=\"EN-US\">mydocker</span>下新建文件夹<span lang=\"EN-US\">tomcat9</span>，进入。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:0;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-bidi-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><span>2、<spantimes new=\"\" roman\"\'=\"\"> </spantimes></span></span><!--[endif]-->下载<span lang=\"EN-US\">jdk8</span>，<span lang=\"EN-US\">tomcat9</span>，新建<span lang=\"EN-US\">c.txt</span>，建立<span lang=\"EN-US\">Dockerfile</span>。<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:0cm;mso-char-indent-count:\n0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">touch c.txt<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:0cm;mso-char-indent-count:\n0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">vim Dockerfile<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:-18.0pt;\nmso-char-indent-count:0;mso-list:l2 level1 lfo2\"><!--[if !supportLists]--><span lang=\"EN-US\" style=\"mso-fareast-font-family:等线;mso-fareast-theme-font:minor-latin;\nmso-bidi-font-family:等线;mso-bidi-theme-font:minor-latin\"><span>3、<spantimes new=\"\" roman\"\'=\"\"> </spantimes></span></span><!--[endif]--><span lang=\"EN-US\">Dockerfile</span>内容为<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:0cm;mso-char-indent-count:\n0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">FROM centos<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:0cm;mso-char-indent-count:\n0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">MAINTAINER zqh&lt;</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"><a href=\"mailto:531500317@qq.com\"><span>531500317@qq.com</span></a><span>&gt;<o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:0cm;mso-char-indent-count:\n0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">#</span><span>把宿主机当前上下文的<span lang=\"EN-US\">c.txt</span>拷贝到容器<span lang=\"EN-US\">/usr/local</span>下<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:0cm;mso-char-indent-count:\n0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">COPY c.txt /usr/local/cincontainer.txt<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:0cm;mso-char-indent-count:\n0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">#</span><span>把<span lang=\"EN-US\">java</span>和<span lang=\"EN-US\">tomcat</span>添加到容器<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:0cm;mso-char-indent-count:\n0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">ADD apache-tomcat-9.0.14.tar.gz\n/usr/local/<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:0cm;mso-char-indent-count:\n0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">ADD jdk-8u201-linux-x64.tar.gz /usr/local/<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:0cm;mso-char-indent-count:\n0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">#</span><span>安装<span lang=\"EN-US\">vim</span>编辑器<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:0cm;mso-char-indent-count:\n0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">RUN yum -y install vim<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:0cm;mso-char-indent-count:\n0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">#</span><span>设置工作访问时候的<span lang=\"EN-US\">WORDKDIR</span>路径<span lang=\"EN-US\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:18.0pt;text-indent:0cm;mso-char-indent-count:\n0\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">ENV MYPATH /usr/local<o:p></o:p></spa